{"article_id":"jYkfOEkOkPuUZrZ7","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The Ted Cruz and John Kasich campaigns announced apparent coordinated strategies","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"to combat Donald Trump in select upcoming primaries -","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"an effort","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"to force an open convention","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"when the Republican National Committee gathers in Cleveland in July .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"In a statement","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"sent out Sunday evening ,","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"the Cruz campaign said","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"it will focus resources on Indiana ,","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"`` and in turn clear the path for Gov . Kasich","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"to compete in Oregon and New Mexico . ''","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"Kasich 's camp offered an inverse statement within minutes ,","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"it will `` give the Cruz campaign a clear path in Indiana ''","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"while focusing on New Mexico and Oregon .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"Both campaigns called on their allies and third-party groups to cooperate with this approach .","depth":2},{"id":16,"text":"Wow , just announced","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"that Lyin ' Ted and Kasich are going to collude","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"in order to keep me from getting the Republican nomination .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"DESPERATION !","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"April 25 , 2016","depth":5},{"id":23,"text":"Lyin ' Ted and Kasich are mathematically dead and totally desperate .","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"Their donors & special interest groups are not happy with them .","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"Sad !","depth":5},{"id":26,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"April 25 , 2016","depth":5},{"id":29,"text":"Indiana 's primary is on May 3 .","depth":4},{"id":30,"text":"Oregon votes on May 17 .","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"New Mexico is one of the states on the final day of the GOP primary calendar , June 7 .","depth":5},{"id":32,"text":"Both the Kasich and Cruz camps say","depth":5},{"id":33,"text":"they will compete","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"to win other contests in the Republican race over the next six weeks","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"- including the five states","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"voting on Tuesday","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"( Pennsylvania , Delaware , Maryland , Connecticut and Rhode Island )","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"or other states down the line ,","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"including Nebraska , West Virginia , Washington , California , Montana , New Jersey , North Dakota and South Dakota .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"At this point , Kasich is mathematically eliminated","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"from earning the 1,237 delegates","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"needed","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"to win the GOP nomination outright .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"Cruz is likely to also be mathematically eliminated","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"if he does as poorly","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"as polls are suggesting on Tuesday .","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"A contested convention has become their only possible path","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"to stop Trump from being the nominee .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":97,"left":64,"right":96,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":64,"left":63,"right":15,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":63,"left":53,"right":62,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":53,"left":50,"right":52,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":50,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":52,"left":2,"right":51,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":51,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":62,"left":58,"right":61